<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>System Update</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0b0f14;
  --card:#11161c;
  --text:#e6edf3;
  --muted:#8b98a5;
  --accent:#10a37f;
  --border:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
}

*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
}

html,body{
  height:100%;
  width:100%;
  background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, #11161c 0%, #0b0f14 60%);
  font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;
  color:var(--text);
  overflow:hidden;
}

.wrapper{
  height:100%;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:24px;
}

.card{
  width:100%;
  max-width:560px;
  background:var(--card);
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius:18px;
  padding:48px 40px;
  text-align:center;
  box-shadow:0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
}

.logo{
  width:40px;
  height:40px;
  margin:0 auto 28px;
  border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--accent);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  font-weight:600;
  font-size:18px;
  color:#000;
}

h1{
  font-size:29px;
  font-weight:600;
  margin-bottom:16px;
  letter-spacing:-0.02em;
}

p{
  font-size:16px;
  color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.6;
  margin-bottom:32px;
}

.time-box{
  background:rgba(16,163,127,0.08);
  border:1px solid rgba(16,163,127,0.25);
  padding:18px 22px;
  border-radius:12px;
  font-size:15px;
  color:var(--text);
  font-weight:500;
}

.footer{
  position:absolute;
  bottom:24px;
  left:0;
  width:100%;
  text-align:center;
  font-size:13px;
  color:var(--muted);
  opacity:0.7;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="logo">T&J</div>
    <h1>tnjwebdesign.ca is Temporarily Unavailable</h1>
    <p>
      tnjwebdesign.ca is currently unavailable due to a scheduled software update.
      We’re performing maintenance to improve system performance and reliability.
    </p>
    <div class="time-box">
      The system will be back online by<br><br>
      <strong>05:00 Zulu (00:00 Local)<br>02-25-2026</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  © 2026 The T&J Company. All rights reserved.
</div>
</body>
</html>
